B. PICTHUG App
Subject to the terms and conditions of this Agreement, you are hereby granted a non-exclusive, limited, non-transferable, freely revocable license to use the App for your personal, private, noncommercial use, and only in accordance with the features of the App as it is marketed by PICTHUG. PICTHUG reserves all rights not expressly granted herein in the App and the PICTHUG IP (as defined below). PICTHUG may terminate this license at any time for any reason or no reason. Commercial Use. You may not use the PICTHUG App for commercial purposes unless you are the copyright holder or you have obtained all necessary rights and licenses to use for commercial purposes all videos, musical works, sound recording, and other material that make up your User Content.
